Zetetic.Security is a .NET assembly that wraps both the standard .NET Rfc2898DeriveBytes class, as well as a C# port of bcrypt, in the System.Security.Cryptography.KeyedHashAlgorithm type to make it compatible with SqlMembershipProvider and other framework hash functions.

More information:
zetetic.net/blog/2012/3/29/strong-password-hashing-for-aspnet.html

